@startuml sequence_diagram_4
title OAuth2 — вход через Google
actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "React SPA" as UI
participant "Google OAuth2" as Google
participant "Spring Security\nOAuth2" as SEC
participant "OAuth2successHandler\n(Security)" as Handler
participant "UserRepository\n(Foundation)" as UR
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> UI : Нажать «Войти через Google»
UI -> SEC : GET /oauth2/authorization/google
SEC -> Google : Redirect (client_id, scope)
Google --> User : Страница согласия Google
User -> Google : Подтвердить
Google -> SEC : callback + authorization code
SEC -> Google : Обмен code → access_token
Google --> SEC : access_token, email, name
SEC -> Handler : onAuthenticationSuccess()
Handler -> UR : findByEmail(email)
UR -> DB : SELECT * FROM app_user\nWHERE email=?
DB --> UR : Optional<User>
UR --> Handler : Optional<User>

alt Пользователь существует
  Handler -> Handler : generateJWT(existingUser)
else Новый пользователь
  Handler -> UR : save(newUser GOOGLE)
  UR -> DB : INSERT INTO app_user ...
  Handler -> Handler : generateJWT(newUser)
end

Handler --> UI : Redirect\n{APP_FRONTEND_URL}/oauth2/redirect\n?token=...&userId=...
UI -> UI : Сохранить токен (OAuthRedirect)
UI --> User : Перенаправить на /profile

@enduml
